g>Dankzij de krachtige, oplaadbare batterij geniet je van urenlang sfeervol licht –<strong> zonder gedoe met kabels<\/strong>. Een praktische én stijlvolle oplossing voor elk interieur of horecazaak.<\/p>","text_style":"body"}}},"block_order":["caption_7VEKFV","heading_qt6VrE","text_G4R9yi"],"settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/ChatGPT_Image_6_mei_2025_13_03_31.png","height":"adapt","color_scheme":"background-1","section_color_scheme":"background-1","content_layout":"no-overlap","layout":"text_first","desktop_content_position":"top","desktop_content_alignment":"left","mobile_content_alignment":"left"}},"588f6a03-9251-48aa-a934-da38c979a83d":{"type":"collapsible-content","blocks":{"template--20385125597508__588f6a03-9251-48aa-a934-da38c979a83d-collapsible_row-2":{"type":"collapsible_row","settings":{"heading":"Hoe kan ik de lamp van stroom voorzien?","icon":"none","row_content":"<p>In tegenstelling tot conventionele lampen kan hij van stroom worden voorzien via de meegeleverde universele USB-kabel of via 3 x AA-batterijen (niet meegeleverd), waardoor hij er overzichtelijk uitziet en de flexibiliteit heeft om overal in huis geplaatst te worden.<\/p>","page":""}},"template--20385125597508__588f6a03-9251-48aa-a934-da38c979a83d-collapsible_row-4":{"type":"collapsible_row","settings":{"heading":"Kan ik mijn bestelling retourneren als ik niet tevreden ben?","icon":"none","row_content":"<p>Geen probleem! Neem binnen 30 dagen na ontvangst contact op met de klantenservice, dan helpen wij je verder!<\/p>","page":""}},"template--20385125597508__588f6a03-9251-48aa-a934-da38c979a83d-collapsible_row-3":{"type":"collapsible_row","settings":{"heading":"Hoe hoog is de lamp?","icon":"none","row_content":"<p>De Glow Tree is 45cm hoog<\/p>","page":""}}},"block_order":["template--20385125597508__588f6a03-9251-48aa-a934-da38c979a83d-collapsible_row-2","template--20385125597508__588f6a03-9251-48aa-a934-da38c979a83d-collapsible_row-4","template--20385125597508__588f6a03-9251-48aa-a934-da38c979a83d-collapsible_row-3"],"disabled":true,"settings":{"caption":"","heading_size":"h2","heading_alignment":"center","layout":"none","color_scheme":"background-1","container_color_scheme":"background-2","open_first_collapsible_row":false,"image_ratio":"adapt","desktop_layout":"image_second","padding_top":36,"padding_bottom":36}},"e4394e38-3ec5-4b0f-ad44-21d3ebfbddb6":{"type":"image-with-text","blocks":{"template--20109320978756__e4394e38-3ec5-4b0f-ad44-21d3ebfbddb6-text-1":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"","text_style":"body"}}},"block_order":["template--20109320978756__e4394e38-3ec5-4b0f-ad44-21d3ebfbddb6-text-1"],"disabled":true,"settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/afmetingen.webp","height":"adapt","color_scheme":"background-1","section_color_scheme":"background-1","content_layout":"no-overlap","layout":"image_first","desktop_content_position":"top","desktop_content_alignment":"left","mobile_content_alignment":"left"}},"1257f402-04b3-4e08-93b3-6d6dd0b5f272":{"type":"image-with-text","blocks":{"template--20109320978756__1257f402-04b3-4e08-93b3-6d6dd0b5f272-text-1":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"<h4>Praktisch ingebouwd harnas voor optimale controle<\/h4><p>Met de Dog Jacket krijgt je hond niet alleen een <strong>warme winterjas<\/strong>, <strong>maar ook een ingebouwd tuigje.<\/strong> Geen aparte halsband meer nodig! Het geïntegreerde harnas biedt comfortabele en veilige controle tijdens het lopen. Jouw hond zit veilig en comfortabel in de jas. Praktisch en stijlvol voor de winter!<\/p>","text_style":"body"}}},"block_order":["template--20109320978756__1257f402-04b3-4e08-93b3-6d6dd0b5f272-text-1"],"disabled":true,"settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/gif_4_0d76c123-6c4d-4065-9a4d-51e310d5797c.webp","height":"adapt","color_scheme":"background-1","section_color_scheme":"background-1","content_layout":"no-overlap","layout":"text_first","desktop_content_position":"top","desktop_content_alignment":"left","mobile_content_alignment":"left"}},"debb262c-7966-437e-9293-3d712dea0416":{"type":"image-with-text","blocks":{"template--20109320978756__debb262c-7966-437e-9293-3d712dea0416-text-1":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"<h4>Gezellige hondenjas met een zachte fleecevoering<\/h4><p>Met onze knusse hondenjas, die een <strong>zachte fleecevoering<\/strong> heeft, kan jouw harige vriend het hele jaar door de natuur verkennen. De jas is speciaal ontworpen om jouw hond te beschermen tegen koude wind en lage temperaturen.<\/p>","text_style":"body"}}},"block_order":["template--20109320978756__debb262c-7966-437e-9293-3d712dea0416-text-1"],"disabled":true,"settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/gif_5_63ed069c-2c54-48fa-8145-783b67e53542.webp","height":"adapt","color_scheme":"background-1","section_color_scheme":"background-1","content_layout":"no-overlap","layout":"image_first","desktop_content_position":"top","desktop_content_alignment":"left","mobile_content_alignment":"left"}},"fc7f31b1-4af5-4037-bf99-12ffff6d102e":{"type":"collapsible-content","blocks":{"template--20109320978756__fc7f31b1-4af5-4037-bf99-12ffff6d102e-collapsible_row-1":{"type":"collapsible_row","settings":{"heading":"Zijn de jassen waterdicht?","icon":"none","row_content":"<p>Onze jassen hebben een waterafstotende buitenlaag die lichte regen en sneeuw buiten houdt. Ze bieden een zeer goede bescherming tegen vocht.<\/p>","page":""}},"template--20109320978756__fc7f31b1-4af5-4037-bf99-12ffff6d102e-collapsible_row-2":{"type":"collapsible_row","settings":{"heading":"Kan de jas in de wasmachine?","icon":"none","row_content":"<p>Ja, je kan de jas wassen in de wasmachine. Volg de wasinstructies op het etiket om een optimale verzorging te garanderen.<\/p>","page":""}},"template--20109320978756__fc7f31b1-4af5-4037-bf99-12ffff6d102e-collapsible_row-3":{"type":"collapsible_row","settings":{"heading":"Zijn de jassen geschikt voor alle hondenrassen?","icon":"none","row_content":"<p>Onze jassen zijn verkrijgbaar in verschillende maten en passen op de meeste hondenrassen. Bekijk goed de maattabel om de juiste maat voor jouw hond te kiezen.<\/p>","page":""}},"43f6217f-909e-48c4-a956-cd3983c153ec":{"type":"collapsible_row","settings":{"heading":"Is de jas ook geschikt voor katten?","icon":"none","row_content":"<p>Ja zeker, de jas past ook bij katten, zolang het overeenkomt met de maattabel moet de jas goed passen!<\/p>","page":""}},"template--20109320978756__fc7f31b1-4af5-4037-bf99-12ffff6d102e-collapsible_row-4":{"type":"collapsible_row","settings":{"heading":"Kan ik mijn bestelling retourneren als ik niet tevreden ben?","icon":"none","row_content":"<p>Geen probleem! Neem binnen 30 dagen na ontvangst van de jas contact op met onze klantenservice.<\/p>","page":""}}},"block_order":["template--20109320978756__fc7f31b1-4af5-4037-bf99-12ffff6d102e-collapsible_row-1","template--20109320978756__fc7f31b1-4af5-4037-bf99-12ffff6d102e-collapsible_row-2","template--20109320978756__fc7f31b1-4af5-4037-bf99-12ffff6d102e-collapsible_row-3","43f6217f-909e-48c4-a956-cd3983c153ec","template--20109320978756__fc7f31b1-4af5-4037-bf99-12ffff6d102e-collapsible_row-4"],"disabled":true,"settings":{"caption":"","heading_size":"h2","heading_alignment":"left","layout":"none","color_scheme":"background-1","container_color_scheme":"background-2","open_first_collapsible_row":false,"image_ratio":"adapt","desktop_layout":"image_second","padding_top":36,"padding_bottom":36}},"multicolumn_fAACDz":{"type":"multicolumn","blocks":{"column_C847Qb":{"type":"column","settings":{"title":"30 DAGEN RETOURGARANTIE","text":"<p>Wij staan volledig achter de kwaliteit van onze producten. Mocht je toch niet tevreden zijn, dan bieden we onze <strong>\"niet goed, geld terug garantie\" <\/strong>aan. Jouw tevredenheid is onze prioriteit!<\/p>","link_label":"","link":""}}},"block_order":["column_C847Qb"],"settings":{"title":"","heading_size":"h2","button_label":"","button_link":"","color_scheme":"background-1","image_width":"full","image_ratio":"adapt","column_alignment":"left","columns_desktop":3,"columns_mobile":"1","padding_top":16,"padding_bottom":36}},"collapsible_content_TH9RVB":{"type":"collapsible-content","blocks":{"collapsible_row_6cKHMf":{"type":"collapsible_row","disabled":true,"settings":{"heading":"Hoelang gaat de batterij mee?","icon":"none","row_content":"<p>De batterij van de Lumi-Design Tafellamp gaat ongeveer 8-12 uur mee.<\/p>","page":""}},"collapsible_row_hzDaFH":{"type":"collapsible_row","settings":{"heading":"Hoe wordt de lamp opgeladen?","icon":"none","row_content":"<p>Opladen gebeurt via de meegeleverde USB-C-kabel.<\/p>","page":""}},"collapsible_row_p7ByyN":{"type":"collapsible_row","settings":{"heading":"Is de lamp dimbaar?","icon":"none","row_content":"<p>Ja, de lamp heeft drie lichtstanden (warm, natuurlijk en wit licht) die je eenvoudig aanpast met de touchbediening bovenop.<\/p>","page":""}},"collapsible_row_VpntPw":{"type":"collapsible_row","settings":{"heading":"Hoe lang gaat de batterij mee?","icon":"none","row_content":"<p>De lamp heeft een sterke batterij die tot 12 uur meegaat op een volle lading.<\/p>","page":""}},"collapsible_row_iR7fkf":{"type":"collapsible_row","settings":{"heading":"Wat zijn de afmetingen van de lamp?","icon":"none","row_content":"<p>De lamp is 25 cm hoog en heeft een voet van 10 x 10 cm.<\/p>","page":""}},"collapsible_row_bYjE9K":{"type":"collapsible_row","settings":{"heading":"Is de lamp draadloos?","icon":"none","row_content":"<p>Ja, de lamp is volledig draadloos en werkt op een oplaadbare batterij, waardoor je geen last hebt van snoeren op tafel.<\/p><p><\/p>","page":""}},"collapsible_row_Qig9Gt":{"type":"collapsible_row","settings":{"heading":"Hoe wordt de lamp bediend?","icon":"none","row_content":"<p>De lamp is voorzien van een touchbediening aan de bovenzijde, waarmee je de lamp aan\/uit zet en de lichtstanden aanpast.<\/p>","page":""}},"collapsible_row_7qL3bt":{"type":"collapsible_row","disabled":true,"settings":{"heading":"Is de BottleLight veilig?","icon":"n